<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>BAWIPA CU A TUM THAN LAI CH165</title>
<key>G</key>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Bawipa cu a rung tum than lai, Timh cia in um tuah u, Sunparnak in a
 rung tum lai, Timh cia in um tuah u, Amah cu dinnak Bawi a si, A tlanhmi
 thluachuah a pek lai, Bawi thutdan ah bia a ceih lai, Timh cia in um tuah
 u.

[C1]
   Nu-pi-thi rat tikah naa tim lai maw? Nu-pi-thi rat tikah naa tim lai
   maw? Zing, chun le zan caan zongah, Mei inn zinan rawn cia in, Nu-pi-thi
   rat tikah naa tim cang maw?

[V2]
 Bawipa cu a tum than zau lai, Timh cia in um tuah u, Amah zummi a
 hruai hna lai, Timh cia in um tuah u, Vancung darkhing kha an tum lai,
 Bawipa khamhnak a tlun tikah, Nan meiinn tha tein vang law, Timh cia in
 um tuah u.

[C2]
   Nu-pi-thi rat tikah naa tim lai maw? Nu-pi-thi rat tikah naa tim lai
   maw? Zing, chun le zan caan zongah, Mei inn zinan rawn cia in, Nu-pi-thi
   rat tikah naa tim cang maw?

[V3]
 Bawipa nih bia a ceih dih lai, Timh cia in um tuah u, Muko auhnak
 thawng kan theih lai, Timh cia in um tuah u, Tlangcung le ramkip mi
 vialte, Biaceih awkah a kan auh lai, Amah hmaiah kan dir cio lai, Timh
 cia in um tuah u.

[C3]
   Nu-pi-thi rat tikah naa tim lai maw? Nu-pi-thi rat tikah naa tim lai
   maw? Zing, chun le zan caan zongah, Mei inn zinan rawn cia in, Nu-pi-thi
   rat tikah naa tim cang maw?</lyrics>
<hymn_number>165</hymn_number>
</song>